label: Gumpenhuber, Philippe, approximately 1706-1770. Répertoire de tous les spectacles qui ont été donné[s] au Théâtre[s] de la ville : manuscript, [1758-1759, 1761, 1763] / recueilli par Philippe Gumpenhuber. MS Thr 248-248.3. Houghton Library, Harvard University, Cambridge, Mass.
description: This manuscript, compiled by Philippe Gumpenhuber, contains a repertoire of all the spectacles performed in Vienna during the years 1758-1759, 1761, and 1763. It is held at Houghton Library, Harvard University.
